	(gr_text "FABRICATION SPECIFIC NOTES\n1. VIAS\n	A. ALL VIAS EPOXY FILLED AND CAPPED WITH COPPER.\n2. IMPEDANCE CONTROL\n	A. ALL 0.26MM WIDE / 0.15MM SPACE TRACES ON F.CU MUST BE 50 OHMS SINGLE ENDED. COPLANAR WAVEGUIDE REFERENCED\n		TO IN1.CU.\n	B. SEE IMPEDANCE_CONTROL.XLSX FOR DETAILS.\n3. SOLDERMASK\n	A. COLOR: GREEN\n4. HARD GOLD\n	A. HARD GOLD PLATE EDGE CONNECTOR CONTACTS IN AREA LABELLED {dblquote}HARD GOLD PLATING AREA{dblquote} ON USER.DRAWINGS LAYER.\n	B. HARD GOLD PLATING IS 0.8-1.3UM HARD GOLD OVER 3-6UM ELECTROLYTIC NICKEL.\n	C. PLATE CONTACTS ON BOTH F.CU AND B.CU."
